msgstr "Vaincre un meneur gobelin pour faire fuir sa bande."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:345
#, fuzzy
msgid "Choosing Spells:"
msgstr "Choix des sorts :"

#. [object]
#. Delfador does not yet have a true name; he's only called "apprentice"
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:347
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Before each scenario in this campaign, you will have the opportunity to "
"select which spells to equip for the upcoming battle. Remember, double- or "
"right-click on the apprentice to cast chosen spells!"
msgstr ""
"Avant chaque scénario de la campagne, vous aurez la possibilité de "
"sélectionner les sorts à utiliser pour le combat à venir. Rappelez-vous : "
"double-cliquez ou faites un clic droit sur l’apprenti pour lancer les sorts "
"sélectionnés !"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Methor says this when Delfador stands on their keep. Delfador can only recruit mudcrawlers; Methor recruits mages
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:370
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re not yet a journeyman, apprentice! Your mudcrawlers are not without "
"use, but to recruit mages I’ll need to stand on our keep."
msgstr ""
"Tu n'es pas encore un compagnon, apprenti ! Tes golem de boue ne sont pas "
"inutiles, mais pour recruter des mages, il me faudra me tenir sur notre "
"donjon."

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. Methor says this when Delfador stands on their keep. Delfador can not recruit; Methor recruits mages
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:377
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You’re not yet a journeyman, apprentice! To recruit mages I’ll need to stand "
"on our keep."
msgstr ""
"Tu n'es pas encore compagnon, apprenti ! Pour recruter des mages, je devrai "
"me rendre sur notre donjon."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:389
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:515
#, fuzzy
msgid "New Recruit:"
msgstr "Nouvelle recrue :"

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:390
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The apprentice is the main character of this campaign, but right now he’s "
"not your leader. Methor is your leader, and he can recruit Mages."
msgstr ""
"L’apprenti est le personnage principal de cette campagne, mais pour le "
"moment ce n’est pas lui le commandant. C'est Methor qui peut recruter des "
"mages."

#. [object]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:392
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Mages are deadly ranged attackers, with accurate <i>magical</i> attacks that "
"are difficult to evade. They have few hitpoints and are highly vulnerable in "
"melee combat, so take good care of them!"
msgstr ""
"Les mages sont de puissants combattants à distance, capables de lancer des "
"attaques <i>magiques</i> précises et difficiles à éviter. Leur résistance "
"est faible et ils sont très vulnérables en corps à corps, protégez-les bien !"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:405
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"<i>Rain is purely visual, and has no impact on gameplay. If rain is "
"distracting or reduces performance, you can disable it by opening the "
"Preferences menu (Ctrl-P), selecting “Display”, and unchecking “Animate "
"Map.”</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>La pluie est purement visuelle et n’influence pas le jeu. Si elle vous "
"distrait ou réduit les performances, vous pouvez la désactiver en ouvrant le "
"menu Préférences (Ctrl-P), en sélectionnant « Affichage » et en décochant "
"« Animer la carte ».</i>"

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:494
#, fuzzy
msgid "Run for your lives!"
msgstr "Fuyez pour sauver votre peau !"

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:495
#, fuzzy
msgid "Run! Flee back to the swamp!"
msgstr "Courez ! Fuyez vers le marais !"

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:496
#, fuzzy
msgid "Noooo, $unit.name!"
msgstr "Naaaaan, $unit.name!"

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:497
#, fuzzy
msgid "Flee, flee! $unit.name’s dead!"
msgstr "Fuyez, fuyez ! $unit.name est mort !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#. said in response to goblins running away from the fight
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:504
#, fuzzy
msgid "Cowards!! Fight and die like real orcish warriors!"
msgstr ""
"Bande de froussards !! Combattez et mourez comme de vrais guerriers orques !"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#. said after any living unit dies (both human and goblin)
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:530
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(sigh) More casualties of pointless politics. I joined the order to do some "
"<i><b>good</b></i> in the world..."
msgstr ""
"(soupir) Encore des victimes de politiques absurdes. J’avais rejoint l’ordre "
"pour faire du <i><b>bien</b></i> dans le monde…"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#. Ozgob has lost most of his goblins ('runts'), and is about to charge at Delfador personally
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:543
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I’ve had it with this! Never send a runt to do a warrior’s job. I’ll bring "
"you down myself!"
msgstr ""
"J’en peux plus ! Faut jamais envoyer un bon à rien faire le travail d’un "
"guerrier. Je vais vous régler votre compte moi-même !"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:580
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We’ve accumulated a great deal of gold, apprentice. While my magic is "
"powerful on the front lines, if we’re ever struggling it’s also important "
"that I have the chance to recruit new magi from our keep."
msgstr ""
"Nous avons amassé une grande quantité d'or, apprenti. Si ma magie est "
"puissante en première ligne, si jamais nous rencontrons des difficultés, il "
"est également crucial que j'aie la possibilité de recruter de nouveaux mages "
"depuis notre donjon."

#. [message]
#. Ozgob has died, and any remaining goblins are deserting him
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:608
#, fuzzy
msgid "Run away!"
msgstr "Courez !"

#. [message]: speaker=Ozgob
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:613
#, fuzzy
msgid "Useless... goblins..."
msgstr "Bons à rien de gobelins…"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. King Garard has just appeared, along with a few knights
#. King Garard has just appeared, along with a few knights
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:633
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:671
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Ride forth, knights of Wesnoth! No orc who sets foot on our soil shall leave "
"alive!"
msgstr ""
"En avant, chevaliers de Wesnoth ! Aucun orc qui foulera le pied notre sol ne "
"repartira vivant !"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Garard came to kill the goblins, but Delfador has already done it.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:641
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But what’s this? It seems some magi have beaten us to battle and already "
"slain our foe! I wasn’t making a mistake bringing Alduin into the fold after "
"all. Who commands this detachment?"
msgstr ""
"Mais que vois-je ? Il semble que des mages nous aient devancés et ont déjà "
"éliminé notre ennemi ! Je ne me suis donc pas trompé en faisant appel à "
"Alduin. Qui commande ce détachement ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Methor
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:645
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"(bowing) My Lord, Alduin dispatched these apprentices as response to your "
"war-call. I volunteered to lead them, and I now place my medicinal arts at "
"your service."
msgstr ""
"(s’inclinant) Mon seigneur, Alduin a dépêché ces apprentis en réponse à "
"votre convocation à la guerre. Je me suis porté volontaire pour les mener, "
"et je mets désormais mes arts médicaux à votre service."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:649
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"A healer? Well, we’ll have need of your services soon enough. Follow me back "
"to camp. We attack on the morrow!"
msgstr ""
"Un guérisseur ? Eh bien, nous aurons bientôt besoin de vos services. Suivez-"
"moi au camp. Nous attaquons demain !"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#. Delfador has failed to defeat the goblins. Garard does not respect him.
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:679
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But what’s this? Some pencil-necked magi have beaten us to battle, yet can’t "
"even finish off a few goblins! Bah, go back to Alduin, you scholars have no "
"place in war after all."
msgstr ""
"Mais que se passe-t-il ? Des mages maigres comme des clous nous ont devancés "
"au combat, et ils sont même incapables d’éliminer quelques gobelins ! Bah, "
"retournez à d’Alduin, vous autres érudits n’avez rien à faire à la guerre."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/01_Stirrings_of_War.cfg:683
#, fuzzy
msgid "Now I’ll never make a name for myself..."
msgstr "Maintenant, je n'aurai plus l’occasion de me faire un nom..."

