msgstr "Résoudre le casse-tête <i>inclut de l'XP</i>"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:501
#, fuzzy
msgid "Skip the puzzle"
msgstr "Passer le casse-tête"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#. referencing the events in The South Guard; exaggerated
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:534
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Deoran, I took an exam on you during my second year at Alduin. Is it true "
"you single-handedly beat down a horde of black-magic bandits and saved the "
"south from destruction? You’re practically a folk hero!"
msgstr ""
"Deoran, j'ai passé un examen sur toi pendant ma deuxième année à Alduin. Est-"
"il vrai que tu as, à toi seul, battu une horde de bandits adeptes de la "
"magie noire et sauvé le sud de la destruction ? Tu es pratiquement un héros "
"populaire !"

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#. this is what has happened to Deoran since ending The South Guard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:539
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To some, perhaps. The king was less pleased — Garard is magnanimous towards "
"his favorites, but has little tolerance for failure. I found scant room for "
"advancement within Wesnoth after so much blood spilled in Westin."
msgstr ""
"Auprès de certains, peut-être. Le roi, lui, était moins satisfait — Garard "
"est magnanime envers ses favoris, mais il supporte mal l’échec. J’ai trouvé "
"peu de perspectives d’avancement à Wesnoth après avoir versé autant de sang "
"à Westin."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:543
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But that all happened many years ago. Ambassador to Lintanir is a "
"prestigious position, in name if nothing else, and an opportunity to "
"exercise what I learned from my time amongst the Aethenwood elves. I have "
"come to value my friends here."
msgstr ""
"Mais tout cela s’est passé il y a bien des années. Être ambassadeur à "
"Lintanir est un poste prestigieux, même si c’est surtout une question de "
"titre, et une occasion de mettre en pratique les leçons tirées de mon séjour "
"parmi les elfes de la forêt de l’Aethen. J’ai appris à apprécier les amis "
"que je me suis fait ici."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:547
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"I must confess I look forward to once-again marching in company with others "
"of my own ilk, yet still I hope to return to Lintanir once my war-duty is "
"done."
msgstr ""
"Je dois avouer que j’ai hâte de marcher à nouveau en compagnie d’autres "
"personnes de ma propre espèce, mais j’espère néanmoins revenir à Lintanir "
"une fois mes devoirs militaires accomplis."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:561
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Chantal, we have much to speak about. It is clear you have feelings for the "
"ambassador. Deoran is no fool; if he does not already know, he certainly "
"suspects."
msgstr ""
"Chantal, nous avons bien des choses à aborder. Il est évident que tu as des "
"sentiments pour l’ambassadeur. Deoran n’est pas dupe ; s’il ne le sait pas "
"encore, il le pressent probablement."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:565
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"—who? What? Great-Grandfather, I have no idea what you’re talking about."
msgstr ""
"—Qui ? Quoi ? Arrière-grand-père, je n'ai aucune idée de ce dont tu parles."

#. [message]: speaker=Chantal
#. continuing the "Chantal has feelings for Deoran" conversation, a moment after it ended
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:572
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Okay— fine, yes, but Deoran is a good man! Wise and kind, and quietly "
"bearing his burden of exile, so far away from his people? And he’s <i>human</"
"i>! Even a crusty old elf like you has to admit that round ears and stubble "
"are exotic."
msgstr ""
"Bon, d'accord— mais Deoran est un homme bien ! Sage et gentil, portant en "
"silence son fardeau d’exilé, si loin de son peuple ? Et puis il est "
"<i>humain</i> ! Même un vieux elfe râleur comme toi doit admettre que des "
"oreilles rondes et une barbe de trois jours, c’est exotique."

#. [message]: speaker=Kalenz
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/04_The_Sylvan_Seer.cfg:576
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The lives of men burn brightly, but briefly. Even if he returns to Lintanir, "
"what future could you build together? I will not stop you if you want to "
"pursue this, but I know all-too-well the pain from outliving those you love. "
"Cleodil was just as stubborn as you..."
msgstr ""
"Les vies des hommes brûlent intensément, mais brièvement. Même s’il retourne "
"à Lintanir, quel avenir pourriez-vous bâtir ensemble ? Je ne t'arrêterai pas "
"si tu veux poursuivre cela, mais je connais trop bien la douleur de survivre "
"à ceux que l’on aime. Cleodil était aussi têtu que toi.…"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
