#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:937
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We must defeat these saurians and escape before nightfall, or the main "
"orcish camp will wake and be upon us!"
msgstr ""
"Nous devons vaincre ces sauriens et nous échapper avant la tombée de la "
"nuit, sinon le camp orc principal se réveillera et nous attaquera !"

#. [message]: speaker=$unit
#. I have escaped!
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:950
#, fuzzy
