msgstr "Je me sssuis échappé !"

#. [message]: speaker=$unit
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:951
#, fuzzy
msgid "female^I have essscaped!"
msgstr "Je me sssuis échappée !"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:955
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"One of them has gotten away to warn the orcish army! I hate running from a "
"fight, but we have to retreat..."
msgstr ""
"L'un d'eux a réussi à s'échapper pour prévenir l'armée orque ! Je déteste "
"fuir le combat, mais nous devons battre en retraite..."

#. [message]: type=Orcish Warlord
#. an orc has just woken up and found Delfador fighting saurians
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:972
#, fuzzy
msgid "<i>Yaawwnn</i> ...what’s all this noise about?"
msgstr "<i>Bâillement</i> ...c'est quoi tout ce bruit ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:976
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We’ve taken too long, now it’s nighttime and the orcish camp has awoken! I "
"hate running from a fight, but we have to retreat..."
msgstr ""
"Nous avons trop tardé, la nuit est tombée et le camp orc s'est réveillé ! Je "
"déteste fuir le combat, mais nous devons battre en retraite..."

#. [message]: speaker=Ysaxis
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:994
#, fuzzy
msgid "Cursssesss..."
msgstr "Mauditss..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:1005
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ah-ha, got you!"
msgstr "Ah-ha, je t'ai bien eu !"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07_The_Great_River.cfg:1008
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Victory is won! We have done well to remain undetected — the way forward "
"remains clear. Now onwards to the Swamp of Dread, to find out why these "
"saurians are fighting alongside orcs..."
msgstr ""
"La victoire est acquise ! Nous avons bien fait de faire preuve de discrétion "
"— la voie est dégagée. Maintenant, en route vers le Marais de l'Effroi, pour "
"découvrir pourquoi ces sauriens se battent aux côtés des orques..."

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:4
#, fuzzy
msgid "Weldyn Court"
msgstr "Cour de Weldyn "

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:104
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"“<i>Barren Throne</i>”, “<i>Angel of Ashes</i>”; don’t people have better "
"things to do than gossip all day about this vapid prophecy? I put my trust "
"in steel, not seers."
msgstr ""
"« <i>Trône désert</i> », « <i>Ange des Cendres</i> » ; est-ce que les gens "
"n’ont pas mieux à faire que de bavarder toute la journée sur cette prophétie "
"vide de sens ? Moi, je préfère faire confiance à l’acier, pas aux devins."

#. [message]: speaker=Deoran
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:108
#, fuzzy
msgid "My Liege, I fear you give insufficient weight to—"
msgstr "Sire, je crains que vous ne prêtiez pas assez d'attention à—"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:112
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"And “<i>Sceptre of the Wesfolk</i>” is the worst of it all... as if it’s my "
"fault Haldric’s dwarves lost the accursed thing."
msgstr ""
"et « <i>le Sceptre des Wesfolk</i> », c’est vraiment le comble...... comme "
"si c'était de ma faute si les nains de Haldric ont perdu cet objet maudit."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:114
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Even the wife! Ever since Delfador first told us about that prophecy, all I "
"get from Asheviere is gossip; rumors about nobles and expeditions and "
"treasure-seekers and other such nonsense. What do you make of it all, "
"brother?"
msgstr ""
"Même ma femme ! Depuis que Delfador nous a parlé de cette prophétie, tout ce "
"que j'entends à propos d'Asheviere ne sont que des commérages ; des rumeurs "
"sur les nobles, sur les expéditions et les chercheurs de trésors et autres "
"balivernes. Qu'en penses-tu, frère ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:118
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The Sceptre of Fire may have gone missing years ago, but it is still well-"
"known as Wesnoth’s symbol of kingship, among lords and common-folk alike."
msgstr ""
"Le Sceptre de Feu a peut-être bien disparu depuis des années, mais il "
"demeure un symbole incontesté de la royauté de Wesnoth, reconnu tant par les "
"seigneurs que par le peuple."

#. [message]: speaker=Arand
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:120
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"My spies have heard nothing of these sceptre-hunters. But if they are real "
"and a noble actually manages to find and retrieve the Sceptre, well, such a "
"misfortune could put your claim to the throne in serious jeopardy."
msgstr ""
"Mes espions n'ont rien rapporté concernant ces chasseurs de sceptres. Mais "
"si leur existence est avérée et qu'un noble réussit à retrouver et récupérer "
"ce Sceptre, une telle mésaventure pourrait sérieusement compromettre votre "
"prétention au trône."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:124
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Intrigue and influence, politics and loyalty. I’m lucky to have you, Arand. "
"This isn’t my strength."
msgstr ""
"Intrigue et influence, politique et fidélité. J'ai vraiment de la chance de "
"t'avoir, Arand. Ce n'est vraiment pas mon point fort."

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:128
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"But I use the tools I have. Take General Lionel — there’s a man to rely on! "
"He’s served me loyally for many years; why, I practically trust him more "
"than my own son!"
msgstr ""
"Mais je me sers des moyens dont je dispose. Prenez le Général Lionel — voilà "
"un homme digne de confiance ! Il m’a servi avec loyauté depuis de longues "
"années ; à vrai dire, je lui accorde presque plus de confiance qu’à mon "
"propre fils !"

#. [message]: speaker=Lionel
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:132
#, fuzzy
msgid "(bows)"
msgstr "(s'incline)"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:136
#, fuzzy
msgid "No offense, boy."
msgstr "Sans vouloir t'offenser, mon garçon."

#. [message]: speaker=Eldred
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:140
#, fuzzy
msgid "(scowls)"
msgstr "(fronce les sourcils)"

#. [message]: speaker=Garard
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/07x_Weldyn_Court.cfg:144
#, fuzzy
msgid "Still, these rumors cannot be taken lightly. Something must be done...."
msgstr ""
"Cependant, ces rumeurs ne peuvent pas être prises à la légère. Il faut agir…"

#. [scenario]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/scenarios/08_Ruins_of_Saurgrath.cfg:40
#, fuzzy
msgid "Ruins of Saurgrath"
msgstr "Ruines de Saurgrath"

