#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2461
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Unlike regular units, the apprentice does not use XP to advance, and will "
"instead advance automatically over time as he progresses through the story. "
"The apprentice’s XP is useful for casting spells, but raising him to maximum "
"XP has no special effect."
msgstr ""
"Contrairement aux unités normales, l’apprenti n’utilise pas de points "
"d’expérience pour progresser. Il évolue automatiquement au fil du temps à "
"mesure qu’il avance dans l’histoire. Les points d’expérience de l’apprenti "
"servent uniquement à lancer des sorts ; les amener au maximum n’a aucun "
"effet particulier."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2471
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Unlike regular units, Delfador does not use XP to advance, and will instead "
"advance automatically over time as he progresses through the story. "
"Delfador’s XP is useful for casting spells, but raising him to maximum XP "
"has no special effect."
msgstr ""
"Contrairement aux unités classiques, Delfador ne dépense pas d'XP pour "
"progresser ; sa progression est automatique et se fait au fil de l'histoire. "
"L'XP de Delfador lui permet de lancer des sorts, mais atteindre le maximum "
"d'XP n'a aucun effet particulier."

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2487
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Congratulations on your journeymanship, $unit.name! Those fireballs are "
"breathtaking! ...now how long until I’m allowed to cast them too?"
msgstr ""
"Félicitations pour ton compagnonage, $unit.name ! Ces boules de feu sont "
"époustouflantes ! … et maintenant, dans combien de temps pourrai-je en "
"lancer moi aussi ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Delfador
#: data/campaigns/The_Deceivers_Gambit/utils/spellcasting.cfg:2498
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Congratulations, $unit.name! Your journeyman’s robes look breathtaking. Now "
"if only Methor would award me mine too ...in red, of course."
msgstr ""
"Félicitations, $unit.name ! Votre toge de compagnon est magnifique. Si "
"seulement Methor pouvait m'en décerner une aussi… en rouge, bien sûr."

